EN: There is a concert on the square tonight.
ZH: 这个广场是本市的地标之一。
EN: This square is one of the landmarks of the city.
ZH: 我们经常在广场上散步。
EN: We often take walks on the square.
ZH: 广场上有一个喷泉，非常漂亮。
EN: There is a fountain on the square, which is very beautiful.
